data.description: With 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths, this home provides ample space for comfortable living. The primary bathroom stands out with its spacious 4x9 shower, equipped with 3 shower heads and a comfortable seat. The front porch features a photo-electric eye, enhancing security. It is covered and boasts maintenance-free posts, ensuring a hassle-free upkeep. Additionally, the presence of two Ring doorbells ensures you'll never miss a visitor. The roof, a vital component of the exterior, was recently replaced in 2021. The kitchen is a chef's dream, offering a 7' island, double ovens, a cooktop, microwave, separate prep sink, and thoughtful storage solutions like lazy Susan in each corner cabinet and pull-out drawers for pots and pans. A dedicated cabinet for trash and a new refrigerator with Wi-Fi capabilities, capable of making cubed and large ball ice, add to the kitchen's functionality. A pantry completes this well-appointed culinary space. A 20x30 sunroom is a highlight of the property.
